Specular Difference plugin for GIMP.

This plugin allows specular light in a scene to be isolated by 
subtracting an image filtered by a polariser from an unfiltered one. 
More details can be found at:

  http://registry.gimp.org/node/25020

The plugin can be installed on a Linux system with gimptool utility.

